\f2\i \cf2 Transhuman Space}} and the more {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SpeculativeFiction"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Speculative Fiction}} works of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JulesVerne"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Jules Verne}} fall in this subclass.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb200\partightenfactor0

